If you run the above code snippet, you'll see that you don't have any options menu created. However, if you don't set the up affordance by commenting the line {code}this.getActivity().actionBar.setDisplayHomeAsUp(true){code}, you will get your action. Those two features should be working at the same time without any problem.

I hope it's clearer this way.

